tracklet showcase — third-party attribution
============================================

The M1 result displayed by showcase/index.html is derived from a real, public
telescope frame:

    "Raw FITS ... BlueWalker 3" (DDOTI / OAN-SPM)
    Zenodo record 8102655 — DOI 10.5281/zenodo.8102655
    Licence: CC-BY-4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)

The frame is a 10-second DDOTI exposure of BlueWalker 3 (NORAD 53807), taken
2022-11-18 02:47 UTC from OAN-SPM, San Pedro Martir, Mexico.

This NOTICE is committed unconditionally. It attributes the SOURCE FRAME the M1
result is derived from, whether or not the optional overlay thumbnail
(showcase/assets/m1_overlay.png) is present — the page degrades to numbers-only
without the thumbnail, but the source-frame attribution still applies.

The frame itself is NOT redistributed in this repository (multi-MB binaries stay
gitignored and are fetched on demand); only the precomputed numeric result of
running the tracklet pipeline on it is committed, in showcase/data/m1_result.json.

